The paper deals with mechanism design for procurement auctions, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT). The focus is on maximizing symmetric submodular functions, which is a topic in discrete optimization (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also proposes algorithms and analyzes their approximation ratios, which is a topic in theoretical computer science (cs.TH) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses budget constraints, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT).
